{"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/stylemanager\/addgeojsonsourcefeatures(forsourceid:features:dataid:)"]}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Add additional features to a GeoJSON style source.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleManager\/addGeoJSONSourceFeatures(forSourceId:features:dataId:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addGeoJSONSourceFeatures","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"forSourceId","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sourceId","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"features"},{"text":": [","kind":"text"},{"text":"Feature","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/Feature","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10MapboxMaps7Featurea"},{"text":"], ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"dataId"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"? = nil)","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"sourceId","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The identifier of the style source."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An array of GeoJSON features to be added to the source."}]}],"name":"features"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An arbitrary string used to track the given GeoJSON data."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"dataId"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The add operation will be scheduled and applied on a GeoJSON serialization queue.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In order to capture events when actual data is drawn on the map please refer to Events API"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and listen to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"onSourceDataLoaded"},{"type":"text","text":" (optionally pass the "},{"code":"dataId","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter to filter the events)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"or ","type":"text"},{"code":"onMapLoadingError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" with ","type":"text"},{"code":"type = metadata","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if data parsing error has occurred.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Partially updating a GeoJSON source is not compatible with using shared cache and generated IDs.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is important to ensure that every feature in the GeoJSON style source, as well as the newly added"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"feature, has a unique ID (or a unique promote ID if in use). Failure to provide unique IDs will result","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"map-loading-error"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The method allows the user to provide a data ID, which will be returned as the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dataId"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"type":"text","text":" event. However, it’s important to note that multiple partial updates can be queued"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for the same GeoJSON source when ongoing source parsing is taking place. In these cases, the partial"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"updates will be applied to the source in batches. Only the data ID provided in the most recent call within"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"each batch will be included in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"text":" event. If no data ID is provided in the most recent","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"call, the data ID in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"type":"text","text":"event will be null."}]}],"style":"note"},{"type":"aside","name":"Throws","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleError"},{"type":"text","text":" if there is a problem adding features to the source."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/Overview","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/Style","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleManager"]]},"metadata":{"title":"addGeoJSONSourceFeatures(forSourceId:features:dataId:)","modules":[{"name":"MapboxMaps"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"addGeoJSONSourceFeatures","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"forSourceId"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"features"},{"kind":"text","text":": ["},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10MapboxMaps7Featurea","text":"Feature","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"], "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"dataId"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"exter